title: Quick Take: March 22 Contests
description: 229 delegates were at stake on Tuesday with primaries/caucuses in Arizona, Idaho, and Utah. Campaign reporter Scott Detrow and political editor Domenico Montanaro wrap up some of the results. For more, find the NPR Politics team on Twitter, at nprpolitics.org, or write the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
